flowchart TD
    Start([Start: Multi-Party Decentralized Setup]) --> NoiseSetup[Noise Protocol: Peer Discovery & Handshake]

    NoiseSetup --> Connect1[Coordinator establishes<br/>Noise channel with Attestor 1]
    NoiseSetup --> Connect2[Coordinator establishes<br/>Noise channel with Attestor 2]
    NoiseSetup --> Connect3[Coordinator establishes<br/>Noise channel with Attestor 3+]

    Connect1 --> AuthPeers{All Peers<br/>Authenticated?}
    Connect2 --> AuthPeers
    Connect3 --> AuthPeers

    AuthPeers -->|Yes| Phase1[Phase 1: Setup & Key Generation]
    AuthPeers -->|No| NoiseSetup

    Phase1 --> Cmd1[Coordinator broadcasts via Noise:<br/>COMMAND: Upload DARs]

    Cmd1 --> Step1_0A[Attestor 1: Upload DARs<br/>Send ACK to Coordinator]
    Cmd1 --> Step1_0B[Attestor 2: Upload DARs<br/>Send ACK to Coordinator]
    Cmd1 --> Step1_0C[Attestor 3+: Upload DARs<br/>Send ACK to Coordinator]

    Step1_0A --> Cmd2[Coordinator receives all ACKs<br/>Broadcasts via Noise:<br/>COMMAND: Generate Keys]
    Step1_0B --> Cmd2
    Step1_0C --> Cmd2

    Cmd2 --> Step1_1A[Attestor 1: Generate Keys<br/>Output: keys + participant ID]
    Cmd2 --> Step1_1B[Attestor 2: Generate Keys<br/>Output: keys + participant ID]
    Cmd2 --> Step1_1C[Attestor 3+: Generate Keys<br/>Output: keys + participant ID]

    Step1_1A --> Send1A[Attestor 1 sends via Noise:<br/>attestor-public-keys.bin<br/>participant-id.bin]
    Step1_1B --> Send1B[Attestor 2 sends via Noise:<br/>attestor-public-keys.bin<br/>participant-id.bin]
    Step1_1C --> Send1C[Attestor 3+ sends via Noise:<br/>attestor-public-keys.bin<br/>participant-id.bin]

    Send1A --> Collect1{Coordinator receives<br/>all keys & IDs via Noise}
    Send1B --> Collect1
    Send1C --> Collect1

    Collect1 --> Phase2[Phase 2: Proposal Creation]

    Phase2 --> Step1a[Coordinator: Create Proposals<br/>DNS, P2P, PTK proposals]

    Step1a --> Dist1[Coordinator distributes via Noise:<br/>dns_proto.bin to all attestors]

    Dist1 --> Phase3[Phase 3: Topology Signing & Submission]

    Phase3 --> Step2A[Attestor 1: Sign DNS Proposal]
    Phase3 --> Step2B[Attestor 2: Sign DNS Proposal]
    Phase3 --> Step2C[Attestor 3+: Sign DNS Proposal]

    Step2A --> Send2A[Attestor 1 sends via Noise:<br/>signed-dns-proposal-1.bin]
    Step2B --> Send2B[Attestor 2 sends via Noise:<br/>signed-dns-proposal-2.bin]
    Step2C --> Send2C[Attestor 3+ sends via Noise:<br/>signed-dns-proposal-3.bin]

    Send2A --> Collect2{Coordinator receives<br/>all DNS signatures via Noise}
    Send2B --> Collect2
    Send2C --> Collect2

    Collect2 --> Step2a[Coordinator: Submit DNS Proposal<br/>Aggregate & submit to Canton<br/>Wait for propagation]

    Step2a --> Notify1[Coordinator broadcasts via Noise:<br/>STATUS: DNS submitted successfully]

    Notify1 --> Dist2[Coordinator distributes via Noise:<br/>p2p_proto.bin + ptk_proto.bin]

    Dist2 --> Step3A[Attestor 1: Sign P2P/PTK Proposals]
    Dist2 --> Step3B[Attestor 2: Sign P2P/PTK Proposals]
    Dist2 --> Step3C[Attestor 3+: Sign P2P/PTK Proposals]

    Step3A --> Send3A[Attestor 1 sends via Noise:<br/>signed-p2p-ptk-proposals-1.bin]
    Step3B --> Send3B[Attestor 2 sends via Noise:<br/>signed-p2p-ptk-proposals-2.bin]
    Step3C --> Send3C[Attestor 3+ sends via Noise:<br/>signed-p2p-ptk-proposals-3.bin]

    Send3A --> Collect3{Coordinator receives<br/>all P2P/PTK signatures via Noise}
    Send3B --> Collect3
    Send3C --> Collect3

    Collect3 --> Step3a[Coordinator: Submit Final Proposals<br/>Aggregate & submit P2P + PTK<br/>Wait for propagation]

    Step3a --> Notify2[Coordinator broadcasts via Noise:<br/>STATUS: Topology fully configured]

    Notify2 --> Phase4[Phase 4: Ledger Submission Preparation]

    Phase4 --> Step3b[Coordinator: Prepare Submissions<br/>3 prepared submissions:<br/>1. CBTCGovernanceRules<br/>2. CBTCDepositAccountRules<br/>3. CBTCWithdrawAccountRules]

    Step3b --> Dist3[Coordinator distributes via Noise:<br/>prepared-submission-1/2/3.bin]

    Dist3 --> Phase5[Phase 5: Ledger Signing & Execution]

    Phase5 --> Step4A[Attestor 1: Sign Submissions<br/>Sign 3 submission hashes]
    Phase5 --> Step4B[Attestor 2: Sign Submissions<br/>Sign 3 submission hashes]
    Phase5 --> Step4C[Attestor 3+: Sign Submissions<br/>Sign 3 submission hashes]

    Step4A --> Send4A[Attestor 1 sends via Noise:<br/>submission-signatures-1.bin]
    Step4B --> Send4B[Attestor 2 sends via Noise:<br/>submission-signatures-2.bin]
    Step4C --> Send4C[Attestor 3+ sends via Noise:<br/>submission-signatures-3.bin]

    Send4A --> Collect4{Coordinator receives<br/>all submission signatures via Noise}
    Send4B --> Collect4
    Send4C --> Collect4

    Collect4 --> Step5[Coordinator: Execute Submissions<br/>Aggregate signatures & execute<br/>Wait for contracts in ACS]

    Step5 --> Notify3[Coordinator broadcasts via Noise:<br/>STATUS: Setup complete!<br/>Decentralized party configured]

    Notify3 --> Disconnect[Noise Protocol: Secure disconnect<br/>All channels closed]

    Disconnect --> Complete([Complete: Decentralized Party<br/>Fully Configured])

